===============================================================
 Ruby interface of Tkrzw
================================================================

Please read the following documents.

  COPYING           - license
  CONTRIBUTING.md   - how to contribute

You should install the latest version of Tkrzw to make sure the
compatibility.

To build the library, Ruby 2.5 or later version is required.
Then, run these commands.

  ruby extconf.rb
  make
  ruby check.rb
  sudo make install

See https://dbmx.net/tkrzw/api-ruby/ for details of the API.

Thanks.

== END OF FILE ==
